&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint to the role of CMC Office Manager, to manage the CMC office operations and help desk. This is a hands on role that requires considerable attention to deatil. You will be responsible for providing day to day office operational duties, including line management duties, performance reporting and will report up to the CMC Management Team.&lt;br /&gt;The post will suit a dynamic, self-motivated and ambitious individual who is able to perform highly effective operational functions as well as implement change. You must be highly organised, an outstanding communicator and able to deal effectively and efficiently with multiple, concurrent activities, tight deadlines and a wide range of stakeholders. Reporting to the CMC General Manager, the post holder must be capable of working minimal need for continual supervision. If this is you, we look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nick Tigere - General Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;nick.tigere@rmh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
